# app/views/order_mailer/confirmation.text.erb

XSpaceGrow - Order Confirmation
================================

Hi <%= @user.display_name || @user.email.split('@').first.capitalize %>,

Thank you for your order! We've received your payment and are preparing your order for fulfillment.

ORDER DETAILS
-------------
Order Number: #<%= @order_number %>
Order Date: <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>
Status: Paid
Total: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", @total) %>

ITEMS ORDERED
-------------
<% @line_items.each do |item| %>
<%= item.product.name %>
<%= item.product.description %>
Quantity: <%= item.quantity %>
Price: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", item.subtotal) %>
<% if item.product.device? %>
** Device - Activation Required **
<% end %>

<% end %>

<% if @device_items.any? %>
DEVICE ACTIVATION REQUIRED
--------------------------
You have purchased device(s) that require activation. You'll receive separate emails with detailed activation instructions for each device.

<% end %>
WHAT'S NEXT?
------------
1. Your payment has been processed successfully
<% if @device_items.any? %>
2. You'll receive device activation instructions via email shortly
3. Follow the activation instructions to connect your devices
<% end %>
4. Access your dashboard to monitor your devices

NEED HELP?
----------
If you have any questions about your order, please contact us:
Email: support@spacegrow.local

